Leaders will exchange views on taking the multifaceted bilateral ties forward with mutual commitment to foster growth, widen collaboration in various fields and deepen convergences on regional & global issues.

The 74th Republic Day of India was celebrated at the Embassy with great enthusiasm and patriotic fervour. Amb Dr Neena Malhotra hoisted the tricolour and read out the President's message followed by cultural performances. @meaindia @indiplomacy 
#republicday2023

Adding momentum to India-Italy ties!

PM Giorgia Meloni of Italy arrives in New Delhi on a State Visit.  MoS Ministry of Health Dr. Bharati Pravin Pawar welcomed PM Meloni at the airport. 

The visit coincides with 75 years of establishment of our diplomatic relations.

PM Meloni will also be the Chief Guest and Keynote Speaker at #RaisinaDialogue2023.

Repost @meaindia

The joyous Holi celebration at the Embassy witnessed enthusiastic participation of members of the Diplomatic corps, community, expats & students to experience the vibrant Indian culture. @meaindia @indiplomacy
